snippet.title: Maskerade: The Deadpan Cry - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Official trailer of Maskerade: The Deadpan Cry, an indie horror game.
Available in Steam and Itchio in 2022.
Developed by Spiky Duck, an Spanish college team of 15 people.

#horrorgaming #steam #maskerade
